{%- comment -%} Services page — full catalogue of EvoTech Digital offerings. Assign via Pages → Template picker. {%- endcomment -%}
{% render 'evotech-breadcrumbs' %}

<section class="evo-svc">
  <header class="evo-svc__head">
    <p class="evo-svc__eyebrow">SERVICES · PERTH MSP</p>
    <h1 class="evo-svc__title">Everything your business needs to run secure, modern IT.</h1>
    <p class="evo-svc__lede">From helpdesk and endpoint management to cyber security, cloud migration and custom AI agents — one accountable Perth team across the full stack.</p>
    <div class="evo-svc__cta-row">
      <a class="evo-svc__btn evo-svc__btn--primary" href="/pages/contact">Book a 20-min call</a>
      <a class="evo-svc__btn evo-svc__btn--ghost" href="tel:+61466911816">Call +61 466 911 816</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="evo-svc__grid">
    <article class="evo-svc__card" id="managed-it">
      <div class="evo-svc__ico">01</div>
      <h2>Managed IT Services</h2>
      <p>24×7 monitoring, proactive patching, endpoint management and helpdesk. Named engineers, Perth business hours, documented runbooks and SLAs you can read.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>RMM + patch management across Windows, macOS, Linux</li>
        <li>Helpdesk + remote support (AWST hours)</li>
        <li>Asset lifecycle &amp; warranty tracking</li>
        <li>Monthly reporting + quarterly business review</li>
      </ul>
      <a class="evo-svc__more" href="/pages/contact?topic=Managed+IT">Talk to us about Managed IT →</a>
    </article>

    <article class="evo-svc__card" id="cyber-security">
      <div class="evo-svc__ico">02</div>
      <h2>Cyber Security &amp; Essential 8</h2>
      <p>ACSC Essential 8-aligned hardening, MFA rollout, immutable backups, EDR and incident response. Uses our in-house <strong>SentryOps SIEM</strong> and <strong>Essential 8 Compass</strong> for live compliance scoring.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Essential 8 maturity assessment + gap remediation</li>
        <li>MFA, Conditional Access, privileged access management</li>
        <li>EDR + 24×7 SOC monitoring via SentryOps</li>
        <li>Immutable backups + tabletop incident response drills</li>
      </ul>
      <a class="evo-svc__more" href="/pages/contact?topic=Cyber+Security">Book a security review →</a>
    </article>

    <article class="evo-svc__card" id="cloud-m365">
      <div class="evo-svc__ico">03</div>
      <h2>Cloud &amp; Microsoft 365</h2>
      <p>Tenant design, migration and day-2 ops for Microsoft 365, Azure, Intune and Entra ID. We migrate mailboxes, files and identities with zero-downtime runbooks.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Exchange → M365 migration (mail, calendar, OneDrive)</li>
        <li>Intune device management + autopilot onboarding</li>
        <li>Entra ID + Conditional Access + SSO</li>
        <li>SharePoint / Teams architecture &amp; governance</li>
      </ul>
      <a class="evo-svc__more" href="/pages/contact?topic=Cloud+Migration">Plan your cloud move →</a>
    </article>

    <article class="evo-svc__card" id="vcio">
      <div class="evo-svc__ico">04</div>
      <h2>vCIO &amp; IT Consulting</h2>
      <p>Quarterly technology roadmaps, budget planning, vendor management and board-ready reports. Powered by our <strong>vCIO Console</strong> — every decision tied to a KPI.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>3-year IT roadmap + CapEx / OpEx planning</li>
        <li>Vendor consolidation &amp; contract review</li>
        <li>Compliance posture (Essential 8, ISO 27001, APRA CPS 234)</li>
        <li>Quarterly business review with named vCIO</li>
      </ul>
      <a class="evo-svc__more" href="/pages/contact?topic=vCIO">Request a vCIO intro →</a>
    </article>

    <article class="evo-svc__card" id="network">
      <div class="evo-svc__ico">05</div>
      <h2>Network Design &amp; Security</h2>
      <p>SD-WAN, firewalls, Wi-Fi 6/6E and segmented VLANs. Real-time observability via our <strong>NetPulse</strong> platform — no more "the internet is slow" mysteries.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Site survey + greenfield design (offices, warehouses, sites)</li>
        <li>Fortinet / Meraki / Ubiquiti deployment &amp; tuning</li>
        <li>Network segmentation + zero-trust access</li>
        <li>Continuous performance monitoring via NetPulse</li>
      </ul>
      <a class="evo-svc__more" href="/pages/contact?topic=Network">Scope a network upgrade →</a>
    </article>

    <article class="evo-svc__card evo-svc__card--featured" id="ai-agents">
      <div class="evo-svc__ico">06</div>
      <div class="evo-svc__badge">NEW</div>
      <h2>Custom AI Agents</h2>
      <p>Bespoke AI agents built on our <strong>EvolveAI Engine</strong> &amp; <strong>EvolveAI Autopilot</strong> — tuned on your data, deployed into your workflows, with auditable guardrails.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Customer support copilots (Zendesk, Freshdesk, Intercom)</li>
        <li>Back-office automations (invoicing, ticketing, triage)</li>
        <li>Knowledge agents grounded on SharePoint / Notion / Confluence</li>
        <li>SOC 2-ready logging, redaction and human-in-the-loop review</li>
      </ul>
      <a class="evo-svc__more" href="/pages/contact?topic=AI+agent">Scope an AI agent build →</a>
    </article>

    <article class="evo-svc__card" id="procurement">
      <div class="evo-svc__ico">07</div>
      <h2>Hardware Procurement</h2>
      <p>Enterprise laptops, desktops, servers and networking — sourced through authorised Australian distributors. Powered by our <strong>ProcureIQ</strong> quoting engine.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Dell, HP, Lenovo, Apple, Microsoft Surface, Cisco, Fortinet</li>
        <li>Device standardisation + fleet lifecycle planning</li>
        <li>Warranty registration &amp; asset tagging on arrival</li>
        <li>Zero-touch deployment via Intune Autopilot</li>
      </ul>
      <a class="evo-svc__more" href="/pages/it-procurement-perth">Submit a purchase request →</a>
    </article>

    <article class="evo-svc__card" id="managed-print">
      <div class="evo-svc__ico">08</div>
      <h2>Managed Print Services</h2>
      <p>Fleet printers, automatic toner replenishment, secure release printing and per-page billing. Fewer help-desk tickets, lower per-page cost.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Fleet audit + right-sized replacement plan</li>
        <li>Secure pull-printing (PaperCut / uniFLOW)</li>
        <li>Automatic consumables + break-fix SLA</li>
        <li>Per-page reporting + chargeback by cost centre</li>
      </ul>
      <a class="evo-svc__more" href="/pages/contact?topic=Managed+Print">Ask about print →</a>
    </article>
  </div>

  <section class="evo-svc__why">
    <h2>Why Perth businesses choose EvoTech</h2>
    <div class="evo-svc__why-grid">
      <div><strong>Local accountability.</strong> Named Perth engineers, AWST hours, quarterly vCIO reviews.</div>
      <div><strong>We run the stack we sell.</strong> Our own SIEM, vCIO console and Essential 8 tooling watch every tenant.</div>
      <div><strong>SLAs you can read.</strong> Plain-English response times, documented runbooks, monthly reports.</div>
      <div><strong>Outcomes, not hours.</strong> Everything tied to an Essential 8 score, uptime target, or business KPI.</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- if page.content != blank -%}
    <div class="evo-svc__extra rte">{{ page.content }}</div>
  {%- endif -%}

  <div class="evo-svc__cta">
    <div>
      <p class="evo-svc__label">READY TO TALK</p>
      <h2 class="evo-svc__cta-title">One intro call. Zero obligation.</h2>
      <p class="evo-svc__cta-lede">Tell us what you're working on — we'll come back within one business day with a plain-English plan, scope and price.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="evo-svc__cta-btns">
      <a class="evo-svc__btn evo-svc__btn--primary" href="/pages/contact">Book a 20-min call</a>
      <a class="evo-svc__btn evo-svc__btn--ghost" href="/collections/all">Browse products</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

